New Records: Victor Wembanyama scored a career-high 50 points
Wembanyama set a personal record for 3-pointers in a game with 7
Wembanyama became the only San Antonio player ever to make at least 6 shots from beyond the arc in 3 consecutive contests
Key Match Events: The Spurs finished the third quarter with a 23-6 run to take a 108-91 lead
Washington made a spirited comeback in the final minutes, cutting the lead to 5 points with 23.4 seconds left but ran out of time
